RuinExplorers - MainEngine

Current Bugs:
- crashes when trying to do air-combo (reason is that the attack animation on keyframe 6 (attack 7) sets setanygoto 11, so the next time attack is pressed any animation should play frame 11. but in midair we are using the fly animation which does have a frame 11)

